Lita Chevret https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lita_Chevret 0 Lita Chevret (May 27, 1908 – May 23, 2001) was an American actress who began her career at the genesis of sound films. She appeared in over 60 films between 1929 and 1940, although in most of those she had small or non-billed parts.
